{"tid":538741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"休班警強姦罪成囚5年半 求情理由：無法再儆惡懲奸","createTime":"2018-01-24T01:50:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-24T13:37:42.000Z","uid":39464,"like":191,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":100,"replies":[{"pid":"2f92cbff3000c64ac5c5d047a8d3ac8c71aac29c","tid":538741,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T01:50:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180123/large/1516722241_f4e2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180123%2Flarge%2F1516722241_f4e2.jpg&h=0933e876&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以首名從警校畢業兼獲頒「銀雞頭」的警員，趁女網友飲醉酒將對方帶到酒店強姦，令女方懷孕，並「走數」未付墮胎費。警員早前被裁定強姦罪成，辯方昨求情透露被告罪成還柙當晚，女友為他誕下骨肉，至今他未見過兒子一面；且他將失去工作，無法實踐儆惡懲奸的抱負，感後悔和內疚。但法官斥被告不但乘人之危，更沒做任何避孕措施，案情嚴重，考慮他孝順、初為人父、過往努力工作，及定罪對他和家人造成打擊，判他入獄5年半。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180124/57746442\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180124%2F57746442&d=8V3KJs1r2MXkCAdtcbJ4fP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=e3dc1493\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180124%2F57746442&h=fde25e71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180124/57746442</a>"},{"pid":"5332f8594fe41fb0a2d82c323b49418d9eba8ef6","tid":538741,"uid":77196,"like":418,"dislike":1,"score":417,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T01:50:56.000Z","msg":"辯方昨求情透露被告罪成還柙當晚，女友為他誕下骨肉，至今他未見過兒子一面；且他將失去工作，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>無法實踐儆惡懲奸的抱負</strong></span>，感後悔和內疚。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要儆惡懲奸咪一槍打爆自己個頭囉，你自己已經係罪犯啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81cb74dbae8ee5aead60e20941106f67cdb2b499","tid":538741,"uid":128223,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T01:51:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"728b630b8a51767810bc6c